        "description": {
          "value": "<p><strong>Trigger&nbsp;</strong>Living creature enters the room;&nbsp;<strong>Effect&nbsp;</strong>The creature automatically becomes Tiny in size as though affected by the @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.PjhUmyKnq6K5uDby]{Shrink} spell<em data-visibility=\"gm\">for 5 minutes</em>. Additionally they must make a <span data-pf2-saving-throw=\"fortitude\" data-pf2-dc=\"32\" data-pf2-traits=\"Polymorph, Transmutation\" data-pf2-label=\"Reduction\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Fortitude</span> save.</p>\n<hr />\n<section class=\"statblock\">\n<p data-visibility=\"gm\"><strong>Critical success</strong>: no additional effect <br /><strong>Success</strong>: the creature is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.fesd1n5eVhpCSS18]{Sickened 1}<br /><strong>Failure</strong>: the creature is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.fesd1n5eVhpCSS18]{Sickened 2}<br /><strong>Critical failure:</strong> The creature is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.fesd1n5eVhpCSS18]{Sickened 2} and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.xYTAsEpcJE1Ccni3]{Slowed 1} as long as it is sickened.</p>\n</section>"
